'''''I Want to Be a Pilot''''' ni  filimi ngufi yasohotse 2006 yegukanye igihembo gikomeye cyane cya Oscars muri 2006<ref>https://www.filmsshort.com/short-film-pages/i-want-to-be-a-pilot-diego-quemada-diez.html</ref>, ituruka muri [[Kenya]] - [[Megizike|Mexique]]  yanditswe inayoborwa na Diego Quemada-Diez<ref>https://moviesthatmatter.nl/en/education/film/i-want-to-be-a-pilot/</ref><ref>https://www.osmaviationacademy.com/blog/10-flight-movies-you-should-see-before-becoming-a-pilot</ref>. Iyi filime imaze kubona ibihembo mpuzamahanga birenga 50<ref>https://www.eyeforfilm.co.uk/review/i-want-to-be-a-pilot-film-review-by-amber-wilkinson</ref><ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/315925-i-want-to-be-a-pilot</ref>, harimo ''igihembo cy’abateze amatwi'' mu iserukiramuco rya Filimi rya Los Angeles,<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/315925-i-want-to-be-a-pilot</ref> kandi yitabiriye iserukiramuco rya firime risaga 200 nka Sundance, Locarno, Telluride, Edinburgh, Amiens, Los Angeles, São Paulo, Manhattan, Silverdocs, Bermuda, San Francisco<ref>https://www.senscritique.com/film/I_Want_to_Be_a_Pilot/41995016</ref> <ref>https://filmeducatie.nl/aan-de-slag/film/i-want-to-be-a-pilot</ref>.

